subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: Ohio State, the last remaining top seed in the West Region, prevailed again, but barely. With a late 3-pointer, the No. 2 Buckeyes squeezed by No. 6 Arizona.
